{"tid":1204204,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)惡靈戰警 懲罰者1-2 私刑教育","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T19:48:07.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52383a623533b1657f4d111362a0e642331c1508","tid":1204204,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:31:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=e41f4ad8\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=72200741\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=1f1b1cdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/ea/Ghost_Rider.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fea%2FGhost_Rider.jpg&h=8009b454&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cf/Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg/220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fcf%2FPunisherwarzoneteaser.jpg%2F220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg&h=08597fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/The_Equalize_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FThe_Equalize_poster.jpg&h=24b407cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.火爆強尼(尼古拉斯&middot;凱奇 飾)原本是一個摩托車特技演員，為了拯救他父親的生命，他將自己的靈魂出賣給惡魔梅菲斯特(彼得&middot;方達 飾)，然而邪惡的勢力竟讓他走火入魔，化身為被詛咒的惡靈戰警，所到之處都引燃熊熊烈焰。而強尼漸漸開始學習控制自己的能力，將無法抑制的憤怒發洩在為非作歹的歹徒身上。但他情不自禁愛上了一個追逐他新聞的女記者(伊娃&middot;曼德絲 飾)，卻因失去靈魂飽受痛楚折磨；而他又將如何對抗更大的惡魔勢力呢?<br />\n<br />\n2.弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特（托馬斯&middot;簡Thomas Jane 飾）的生命中，絕大部分時間都在於死神賽跑。早年在海軍陸戰隊服役，退役後又進入FBI。在槍砲火光中生活了多年之後，弗蘭克不願再整日收到死亡的威脅，家人整日為他擔驚受怕。所以，他決定提前退休與妻兒享受平靜的生活。可是，在最後的一次任務中，卻因意外使一名無辜青年死亡。而這名青年的父親卻是坦帕市的大富商霍華德&middot;桑特（約翰&middot;特拉沃塔John Travolta 飾）。為了給兒子報仇..<br />\n<br />\n3.本想歸隱田園，與家人共度天倫的FBI探員弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特，無奈的在黑幫殺掉妻<br />\n兒之後走向了黑暗復仇的不歸路。弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特大難不死，在悲痛過後開始成為這個城市裡隱秘的&ldquo;懲罰者&rdquo;，在黑暗中打擊那些猖狂的犯罪分子的頭號先鋒。在處決了城內走私行當的龍頭老大之後，懲罰者的名聲鵲起，因此也令城內不少罪犯聞風喪膽，而他也就繼續穿著代表懲罰者的骷髏制服，穿梭在這個充滿罪惡的都市中.....<br />\n<br />\n4.一名為曾為政府工作的前中情局成員化名為羅柏&middot;麥考現住在麻薩諸塞州的波士頓，並在一間五金賣場上班。他協助他的同事朋友拉爾夫減重，以便通過保安考試。麥考答應已過世的妻子，絕不會再回到過去的危險生活。因妻子生前很愛看書，麥考為了達到讀滿100本書，下班後他習慣帶著一包茶包到住家附近一間餐廳看書，日復一日，過著平靜的生活..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=01ce07d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=b7f77d69\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4258eb4e5d4bbf5dda4da6eeaee609b8fafeac","tid":1204204,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb9bcc10145c094b9db1a7337dbbb5857ae5b44","tid":1204204,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e400e0cd89cecdfb8ef7c591335840ababe6e5e","tid":1204204,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eeb51625a6b1fc01074669d27b4e37d7635d4d","tid":1204204,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e63778696ff136a927efd160716bae8951075cb","tid":1204204,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}